text:
GM! Sharing some new updates in Recaster:

- To support Farcaster Auth in Frames V2 and future Sign in with Farcaster, the import recovery phrase feature has been implemented. The recovery phrase is encrypted and stored only on your device.

- New users without a Farcaster account can first authenticate via Apple and create an account for free. The fee is covered by leftover free invites from @newcaster.

- Warpcast labels are also supported and can be clearly seen in the user stats tab.

Recaster will be another independent Farcaster client in 2025ü´°

I‚Äôve worked 10-12 hours a day, 6-7 days a week on DEGEN for the past year‚Äîeven through my honeymoon and holidays. I‚Äôm not asking for thanks, but if you‚Äôre taking your hat off now, it probably was never truly on. The real degens are here for the long haul.

cast.text:
I officially hand over my hat, with much pain, but my confidence has been greatly damaged. üé© 

Sad, because DEGEN has meant a lot to me, but I have been treated like a criminal, after investing a large amount of money in the project.

I will not participate this new season, despite having my bag locked for 3 months. I will not use my allowance. My values ‚Äã‚Äãdo not allow it.

There has been no transparency. I asked why some people who had been banned for the same reason as me, have been unbanned. I have asked about the criteria. I have been ignored. He has not cared at all about the community.

I would like to wish good luck to everyone, and thanks everyone who supported me here. My hat is now off!
